Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:58.09,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}展開なら気分次第
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.38,0:22:00.95,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}刹那へと誘うあなたは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.11,0:22:05.51,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}戯れの中で　自由すぎるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.33,0:22:12.45,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,5000)}
