Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.36,0:22:29.33,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.85,0:22:32.89,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}天使のような　微笑みで
