Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.18,0:22:57.42,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}聖なる魂　あなたを抱きしめたい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.29,0:21:52.63,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2}Won't you show me all your secrets now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.72,0:21:55.28,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}乾澀的心蜷縮在荒漠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:58.09,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}乾澀了它的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.38,0:22:00.95,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}剎那間被誘惑的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.11,0:22:05.51,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在欺騙的愛中沉淪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.33,0:22:12.45,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,5000)\an2}Get out……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.84,0:22:21.41,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}希望揮舞純真無邪之劍的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.61,0:22:27.04,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}盡情地讓疼痛貫穿我的身體
